name: Geomath
tagline: GeoMath - Analytical Geometry Library for Python 3.X -
body:
### Welcome to GeoMath
This is an Analytical Geometry library for Python 3.X, it's called GeoMath and it's, currently, at the version 0.1.1. This will solve all of your problems involving little geometry concepts to hell stuff, so it's a great idea to have Geomath on your hands, so them, you can get anything to work.

### How it Works!
We have a pretty good library for you to get in touch with GeoMath, it's available [here](http://geomath.co/docs/)

### Authors and Contributors
[Vinicius Mesel](http://vmesel.com) - Project Maintainer

[Eduardo Mendes](https://www.github.com/z4r4tu5tr4) - File Structure Creator
